ran away with some woman.

16
00:02:32,291 --> 00:02:34,708
No, Commander Makabe
is not that kind of person.

17
00:02:34,791 --> 00:02:36,666
It's real easy for you
to say that because

18
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:39,500
your daughter
doesn't pilot Fafner.

19
