I'm so sorry...

20
00:02:43,875 --> 00:02:46,875
I thought I was prepared
for this to happen.

21
00:02:46,958 --> 00:02:49,500
Mark Zex and Vier are toast.

22
00:02:49,583 --> 00:02:52,583
Having only Drei
is certainly not enough.

23
00:02:52,666 --> 00:02:54,958
I have absolutely no
idea what more I could

24
