everything happen...

33
00:03:31,125 --> 00:03:34,916
Shoko...
did you feel the same way?

34
00:03:35,875 --> 00:03:38,791
Every time I showed
you the school pictures...

35
00:03:38,875 --> 00:03:42,083
Did you feel lonely like this?

36
00:03:47,583 --> 00:03:49,125
Now I finally understand how

37
00:03:49,208 --> 00:03:53,000
you must have felt
back then Shoko...

38
00:03:53,083 --> 00:03:54,458
I guess that...

39
