I can't complain about
Kazuki and Soshi...

40
00:03:57,541 --> 00:04:00,000
Not anymore at least.

41
00:04:05,833 --> 00:04:08,000
Me?
They want me to pilot?

42
00:04:08,083 --> 00:04:08,791
Really?

43
00:04:08,875 --> 00:04:11,708
Yes.
It's been decided.

44
00:04:13,250 --> 00:04:15,541
Kenji if you don't
think you're up to it,

45
00:04:15,625 --> 00:04:17,166
then I can certainly tell...

46
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:18,208
Yeah!

47
00:04:19,416 --> 00:04:21,541
I'll be able to use this
to pick up chicks!

48
00:04:23,416 --> 00:04:25,708
You're such an idiot!

49
00:04:45,375 --> 00:04:46,416
Darling...

50
